lineStatuses.reason: Route 133 is on diversion due to significant traffic delays at Bank Station from 0600 Monday 20th February until midnight Sunday 30th April. Buses at London Wall are diverting onto Wormwood Street, then turning right onto Bishopsgate, continuing along onto Gracechurch Street before rejoining usual line of route at King William Street. Diversion is in both directions.
